 void Enqueue(
         struct List * list,
         struct Node * node
 );

Function
~~~~~~~~
::

     Sort a node into a list. The sort-key is the field node->ln_Pri.
     The node will be inserted into the list before the first node
     with lower priority. This creates a FIFO queue for nodes with
     the same priority.


Inputs
