     The new node will be inserted before nodes with lower
     priority.


Example
~~~~~~~
::

     struct List * list;
     struct Node * node;

     node->ln_Pri = 5;

     // Sort the node at the correct place into the list
     Enqueue (list, node);


Notes
~~~~~
::

     The list has to be in descending order in respect to the field
     ln_Pri of all nodes.



